  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "Vote: NO\n\n- The revision is genuinely improved over the rejected original (14M ADA → 7.8M ADA, decoupled from TOKEN2049, better oversight)\n- Core objection: $450K revenue against $2.26M budget — treasury absorbs ~80% with no repayment obligation\n- Cardano Foundation's own contribution is only $380K; the organizer asks far more from the treasury than it contributes itself\n- A one-time event produces no compounding infrastructure value — 7.8M ADA at current prices should go to work that persists\n- Encourages resubmission with treasury as a minority funder and a revenue-share or repayment structure"
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}
